PrecisOrder providing for (a) the acceptance of the transfer from the Province of ALBERTA of the administration and control over some 12.7 hectares of land located on KEHEWIN INDIAN RESERVE NO. 123 that were transferred to the Province in 1965 for road purposes, and (b) the setting apart of those lands as a reserve for the use and benefit of the Kehewin Band of Indians.

precis:
